scenes.description: Gigi takes her turn at the Whack-a-Gnome challenge, which quickly devolves into a chaotic chase after she grabs a giant cucumber.
Cecilia attempts the Whack-a-Gnome challenge but refuses to follow the rules, delivering a defiant speech against Smokey instead.
The aftermath of the game where Cecilia expresses her frustration, and the group tries to appease a disappointed Smokey.
Smokey announces the final scores and declares Raora Panthera the overall winner of the 3D collab trials.
Raora makes a special announcement, revealing that the group is about to perform their first live 3D song together.
